Health Statutes using Text Classification and Machine
Learning. In <i>Jurix 2011: The 24th Annual Conference</i>, pp. 73-82
(Katie M. Atkinson ed.) IOS Press 2011.

<li> B. Mohit and R. Hwa. <b>2010</b> Using Variable Decoding Weight
