Translation in the Americas.

<li> F. Liberato, B. Mohit, and R. Hwa. 2010. Improving
Phrase-Based Translation with Prototypes of Short Phrases. In the
Proceedings of the 11th Annual Conference of the NAACL/HLT (short
paper track), Los Angeles, CA.

<li> H. Xue and R. Hwa. 2010. Syntax-Driven Machine Translation as a
Model of ESL Revision. In the Proceedings of COLING 2010: Posters,
Beijing, China. 

<li> J. Albrecht, R. Hwa, and G. E. Marai. <b>2009</b>. Correcting
Automatic Translations through Collaborations between MT and
Monolingual Target-Language Users. In <i>The Proceedings of the 12th
Conference of the European Chapter of the ACL (EACL-2009)</i>, Athens,
Greece.

<li>B. Mohit, F. Liberato, and R. Hwa. 2009. Language Model Adaptation
